title: VA - The Best Latino Carnival In The World...Ever@320
description:
If you are looking for somthing a bit different and fun- try this album
Best Latino Carnival features a very wide variety of music; some well known like Macarena, and La Bamba and some other not so well known ones like Lambada, and La Colegiala, but equally good.
However- after a while, some of the songs start to sound very similar and if you are not a Latin music fanatic, you may find that this is monotonus and boring.
Overall though, this is a fantastic buy, and for the cheap price, it&#039;s and offer you can&#039;t refuse. (Amazon)
